index.name: ckan

name: ckan
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "ckan" %}
{% set version = "2.8.3" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://github.com/ckan/{{ name }}/archive/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 1fdc09f4b1ae3a70d84138118c86eee056695235e5be8c42501c8af6b6679686
  patches:
    - webob.patch

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv "
  skip: True  # [win or py>=35]

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - alembic ==1.0.0
    - babel ==2.3.4
    - bleach ==3.0.2
    - click ==6.7
    - fanstatic >=0.12
    - flask ==1.1.1
    - flask-babel ==0.11.2
    - jinja2 ==2.10.1
    - markdown ==2.6.7
    - passlib >=1.6.5
    - paste >=1.7.5.1
    - PasteScript ==2.0.2
    - polib ==1.0.7
    - psycopg2 ==2.8.2
    - python-magic ==0.4.15
    - pysolr ==3.6.0
    - pylons >=0.9.7
    - python-dateutil >=1.5.0
    - pytz ==2016.7
    - pyutilib ==5.7.1
    - pyyaml
    - repoze.who-friendlyform ==1.0.8
    - repoze.who ==2.3
    - requests ==2.22.0
    - routes ==1.13
    - rq ==1.0
    - simplejson >=3.10.0
    - sqlalchemy-migrate ==0.12.0
    - sqlalchemy ==1.3.5
    - sqlparse ==0.2.2
    - tzlocal ==1.3
    - unicodecsv >=0.9
    - vdm ==0.15
    - webassets ==0.12.1
    - webhelpers ==1.3
    - webob ==1.8.5
    - webtest >=1.4.3
    - werkzeug ==0.15.5
    - zope.interface >=4.3.2

test:
  imports:
    - ckan
    - ckan.plugins

  commands:
    - paster --version
    - paster --plugin=ckan --help

about:
  home: http://ckan.org/
  license: GNU Affero General Public v3 or later (AGPLv3+)
  license_family: AGPL
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: CKAN Software for making open data websites.
  doc_url: https://docs.ckan.org/en/2.8/
  dev_url: https://github.com/ckan/ckan

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - rluria14
    - mwilson8
    - benhuff
